## Remarks  

> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="82187-716"><xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader>类已过时中[!INCLUDE[dnprdnext](~/includes/dnprdnext-md.md)]。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="82187-716">The <xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader> class is obsolete in [!INCLUDE[dnprdnext](~/includes/dnprdnext-md.md)].</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="82187-717">你可以创建一个验证<xref:System.Xml.XmlReader>实例使用<xref:System.Xml.XmlReaderSettings>类和<xref:System.Xml.XmlReader.Create%2A>方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="82187-717">You can create a validating <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> instance by using the <xref:System.Xml.XmlReaderSettings> class and the <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader.Create%2A> method.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="82187-718">有关详细信息，请参阅 <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> 引用页的“备注”部分。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="82187-718">For more information, see the Remarks section of the <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> reference page.</span></span>  

 <span data-ttu-id="82187-719">用户需要进行测试的返回类型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="82187-719">The user needs to test for the returned type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="82187-720">例如，应用于对象的</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="82187-720">For example,</span></span>  

```  
object obj = vreader.SchemaType;  
 if (obj is XmlSchemaType)  
 {  
   XmlSchemaType st = (XmlSchemaType)obj;  
   // use XmlSchemaType object  
 }  
 if (obj is XmlSchemaDatatype)  
 {  
   XmlSchemaDatatype sd = (XmlSchemaDatatype)obj;  
   Type vt = sd.ValueType;  
   // use XmlSchemaDatatype object  
       }  
```  

 <span data-ttu-id="82187-721">如果正在执行 XML 架构验证，`XmlSchemaType`或`XmlSchemaDatatype`对应于正在读取的当前元素。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="82187-721">If XML Schema validation is being performed, the `XmlSchemaType` or `XmlSchemaDatatype` corresponds to the current element being read.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="82187-722">如果正在执行文档类型定义 （DTD 验证），此属性返回`null`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="82187-722">If document type definition (DTD validation) is being performed, this property returns `null`.</span></span>  

 <span data-ttu-id="82187-723">`XmlSchemaDatatype` 返回当前元素或属性，如果是一个简单类型，可以指定对简单类型，如 min 和 max 特殊的验证约束。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="82187-723">`XmlSchemaDatatype` is returned if the current element, or attribute, is a simple type that can specify special validation constraints on the simple types, like min and max.</span></span>  

 <span data-ttu-id="82187-724">`XmlSchemaSimpleType` 返回当前元素或属性，如果是用户定义的简单类型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="82187-724">`XmlSchemaSimpleType` is returned if the current element, or attribute, is a user defined simpleType.</span></span>  

 <span data-ttu-id="82187-725">`XmlSchemaComplexType` 返回当前元素是否是用户定义的 complexType。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="82187-725">`XmlSchemaComplexType` is returned if the current element is a user defined complexType.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="82187-726">属性无法返回此类型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="82187-726">This type cannot be returned by attributes.</span></span>  

> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="82187-727">如果<xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader.ValidationType%2A>已设置到 ValidationType.None，无数据类型信息提供从架构或 Dtd。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="82187-727">If <xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader.ValidationType%2A> has been set to ValidationType.None, no data type information is provided from either schemas or DTDs.</span></span>  

> [!CAUTION]
>  <span data-ttu-id="82187-728">在调用<xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader.Close%2A>，SchemaType 将返回 Null。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="82187-728">After calling <xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader.Close%2A>, SchemaType will return Null.</span></span>  



